<h2>Focus realization and interpretation in Romance and beyond  (Veranstaltungsprojekt)</h2>
<h3></h3>
<hr>
<div class='row-fluid'>
<div class='span8'>
<h4>Allgemeine Angaben</h4>
<dl class='attribute_listing'>
<dt>Projektbeginn</dt>
